-- Magna Says Shareholders Approve Plan to Transfer Control From Stronach
-- Theo Keith
-- 2010-07-23T14:23:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/magna-says-shareholders-approve-plan-to-transfer-control-from-stronach.html

          
          
             Magna International Inc., Canada’s
largest auto-parts maker, will eliminate its dual-class
structure and end founder Frank Stronach’s control of the
company after shareholders approved a reorganization plan.  
 Magna disclosed the results at a special shareholder
meeting in Toronto.  
